ACT:
 Termination of the services of a Principle on probation-Procedure prescribed under section 16 G and regulations 35 to 38 being the same as provided by Article 311(2) of the Constitution of India, the principles which govern such cases of termination should be the same as those underlying Article 311(2) of the Constitution-Interpretation of Statutes-Absence of enquiry contemplated under Regulations 35 & 36 before the termination of the provision casting a stigma is illegal.
 
